title: Custome rDonald T Johnson
text: Great service, courteousness customer service, efficiant shipping department. Oh yes, did I mention the great products. My personal favorite is the sock-eye salmon, baked in parchment paper, blackened, the smoked salmon eaten straight up, on a bagel or made into a salmon and cream cheese spread
